&lt;h3&gt;About &lt;a href=&quot;http://Customer.io&quot;&gt;Customer.io&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over 9,000 companies — from scrappy startups to global brands — use our platform to send billions of emails, push notifications, in-app messages, and SMS every day. &lt;a href=&quot;http://Customer.io&quot;&gt;Customer.io&lt;/a&gt; powers automated communication that people actually want to receive. We help teams send smarter, more relevant messages using real-time behavioral data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hi! I&#39;m Dessa, Associate General Counsel here at &lt;a href=&quot;http://Customer.io&quot;&gt;Customer.io&lt;/a&gt;. We&#39;re hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Legal Assistant&lt;/strong&gt; to help our growing Legal team operate at its best.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a role for someone who loves bringing structure to fast-moving environments — the kind of person who sees a messy folder system and genuinely wants to fix it, who gets excited about finding a better way to route a contract, and who looks at AI tools as a competitive advantage rather than a novelty. You&#39;ll work closely with Legal, Sales, RevOps, and Finance to keep core legal workflows running smoothly, while helping us push the boundaries of how a modern legal team operates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a small but ambitious team, and the work you do here will have real, visible impact from day one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What we value&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own it&lt;/strong&gt; — You take initiative, follow through, and hold yourself accountable. Whether it&#39;s a filing deadline or a process improvement, you don&#39;t let things fall through the cracks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build, don&#39;t just maintain&lt;/strong&gt; — You&#39;re always looking for a better way. You see process gaps as opportunities, not someone else&#39;s problem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use AI like it&#39;s your job&lt;/strong&gt; — Because it is. We expect you to actively experiment with AI tools, identify new use cases, and help us reduce manual work across the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate across boundaries&lt;/strong&gt; — You communicate clearly and work well with people outside the Legal team, whether that&#39;s RevOps, Finance, or a Sales rep who needs a contract update.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Earn trust through the details&lt;/strong&gt; — You&#39;re precise, consistent, and reliable. The Legal team depends on you to keep information accurate and accessible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal Administrative Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Triage and respond to inbound Legal requests and external notices, tracking deadlines so nothing gets missed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own legal calendaring across filings, renewals, and compliance obligations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate invoice processing and vendor payments with Finance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage physical mail, board prep logistics, and note-taking for key Legal meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Document and Knowledge Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
