&lt;li&gt;Manage DocuSign workflows: track envelope status, store completed agreements, keep records clean&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support document migrations, system cleanups, and privacy-related documentation (DPAs, GDPR requests, data flows)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI tools and automation to reduce manual work, improve document retrieval, and increase consistency across Legal processes&lt;/li&gt;
