&lt;p&gt;This is a role for someone who thrives on creating clarity where there isn&#39;t any, can hold a room of opinionated stakeholders accountable without friction, and knows the difference between moving fast and moving smart. If you want to own the operating layer of a growing self-serve business and work alongside teams who are genuinely invested in getting it right, this is the role.&lt;/p&gt;
