&lt;p&gt;You&#39;re a natural connector and systems thinker who knows that the real work happens in the gaps between teams. You don&#39;t wait to be assigned a playbook — you build one. You communicate differently with a PM working through a roadmap decision than you do with a CMO looking for a signal on program progress, and you know exactly when to escalate vs. when to just handle it.&lt;/p&gt;
